links: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n=1,...,1000
prog: (PARI) je=[]; forstep(n=1,301,2, if(isprime(n), n+1,je=concat(je,n^2))); je(PARI) { n=0; forstep (m=1, 10^9, 2, if(!isprime(m), write("b062532.txt", n++, " ", m^2); if (n==1000, break)) ) } [From _Harry J. Smith_, Aug 08 2009]
